{
  "3226660": {
    "name": "魔法与钢铁：英雄牌局",
    "steam_appid": 3226660,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/11651e8485348c1ae4738bb80cea3724.webp?t=1772110064\" width=609 height=28 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">组建英雄小队，构筑强力卡组，掌控中世纪奇幻世界中一场又一场战术对局。规划每一次行动，合理调整站位，运用独特能力，在这款紧张刺激的策略游戏中不断赢得挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/add1030fa0b6ca16e60fb0a0d2ded494.webp?t=1772110064\" width=609 height=28 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/40f44afef5d9a68bb3e303204c35ce55.avif?t=1772110064\" width=609 height=174 /></span><strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/4a04a8de1aebf039fab70b2634ba6020.poster.avif?t=1772110064\" width=698 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/4a04a8de1aebf039fab70b2634ba6020.webm?t=1772110064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/4a04a8de1aebf039fab70b2634ba6020.mp4?t=1772110064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/11651e8485348c1ae4738bb80cea3724.webp?t=1772110064\" width=609 height=28 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">每一次冒险都是全新的体验！将拥有独特能力的英雄组合在一起——从爆发打击、区域控制，到增益、减益以及足以扭转战局的特殊效果。探索英雄之间的协同，释放强力连击，在每一场战斗中发现意想不到的战术。每位英雄都独一无二，而每一套阵容，都能开启截然不同的战略可能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/add1030fa0b6ca16e60fb0a0d2ded494.webp?t=1772110064\" width=609 height=28 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/bd95f06be4c1e3a15224b912f76633fe.avif?t=1772110064\" width=609 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/c25fdaf8af4d42f766f84154b7438a57.poster.avif?t=1772110064\" width=1128 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/c25fdaf8af4d42f766f84154b7438a57.webm?t=1772110064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/c25fdaf8af4d42f766f84154b7438a57.mp4?t=1772110064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/11651e8485348c1ae4738bb80cea3724.webp?t=1772110064\" width=609 height=28 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在每一场战斗中灵活调整你的策略！打造独特的队伍，利用关卡结束后获得的奖励，不断强化你的英雄与卡组。每张卡牌在使用后都会被弃置，因此必须慎重选择出牌时机。当然，卡组构筑本身同样至关重要。通过不断取舍与优化，组合能力、精炼卡组，发掘那些足以决定胜负的协同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/add1030fa0b6ca16e60fb0a0d2ded494.webp?t=1772110064\" width=609 height=28 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/0301d4f0cd836ea5bfb4e2879a07201f.avif?t=1772110064\" width=609 height=174 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/11651e8485348c1ae4738bb80cea3724.webp?t=1772110064\" width=609 height=28 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">迎接每一格都至关重要的战术对决。精准的站位与对战场局势的快速判断，是生存与胜利的关键。每个关卡都会带来全新的地形布局与挑战，不断改变战斗的节奏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/0aef1a4b35dad3016e89d914faffb7d8.poster.avif?t=1772110064\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/0aef1a4b35dad3016e89d914faffb7d8.webm?t=1772110064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/0aef1a4b35dad3016e89d914faffb7d8.mp4?t=1772110064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">敌人的行为各不相同：有的会正面突进，有的远程压制，还有的会制造群体威胁。这让每一个回合都比上一个更加危险。随着威胁不断升级、敌人步步紧逼，唯有周密规划每一次移动，才能真正掌控战场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226660/extras/add1030fa0b6ca16e60fb0a0d2ded494.webp?t=1772110064\" width=609 height=28 /></span></p>",
